<https://w3id.org/rockworx/acq> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Ontology> .
<https://w3id.org/rockworx/acq> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/creator> "RockWorx Aerospace" .
<https://w3id.org/rockworx/acq> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "A BFO/CCO-conformant ontology of the U.S. DoD acquisition lifecycle (DoDI 5000.85) and its 2025 WAS/JFRP reform, with a working SysML v2 integration." .
